@page "/"

<PageTitle>Hyper-V Central</PageTitle>

<h1>Hyper-V Central Management</h1>

<p>
    Central panel for Hyper-V hosts and clusters. Use <strong>Login</strong> to obtain a JWT session,
    then manage registered agents and cluster topology.
</p>

<ul>
    <li>Agents: inventory, heartbeat status, tags, and API endpoints.</li>
    <li>Clusters: group hosts into logical clusters for coordinated actions.</li>
    <li>Direct UI-to-agent calls are supported once you have the agent API URL.</li>
</ul>
